    <string name="help_text">
        Manga Directory Empty Search Query:\n
        \n
        Typing a period character (.) in the Manga Directory\'s search bar will display all results
        for the given genres and completion status. In other words, using the period character and
        searching for no genres and no completion status will display the default search query for
        each source.\n
        \n
        \n
        Uploading Manga Titles for Offline Reading:\n
        \n
        When uploading a title, the folder selected must be in a specific structure; the folder
        selected must only contain other folders, which will be listed as the chapters. The first
        page of the first chapter will be used as the cover image for the title. The chapter folders
        should only contain images (.jpg, .gif, .png, .bmp formats).
    </string>

